== 歷史 ==
第一家英迪格酒店於2004年10月在[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]][[亚特兰大|亞特蘭大]]開業<ref>{{Cite web|title=Atlanta's second Hotel Indigo opens near airport|url=https://www.travelweekly.com/Travel-News/Hotel-News/Atlantas-second-Hotel-Indigo-opens-near-airport|access-date=26 February 2020|author=King|first=Danny|work=Travel Weekly|archive-date=2021-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210807043710/https://www.travelweekly.com/Travel-News/Hotel-News/Atlantas-second-Hotel-Indigo-opens-near-airport|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，第二家酒店則於2005年5月[[伊利诺伊州|伊利諾州]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]][[黄金湖岸历史地区_(芝加哥)|黄金湖岸歷史地區]]開業。 <ref>{{Cite news|author=Ori|first=Ryan|title=Gold Coast's Hotel Indigo getting new name: Claridge House|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/columns/ryan-ori/ct-biz-hotel-indigo-redevelopment-ryan-ori-20180418-story.html|accessdate=26 February 2020|publisher=The Chicago Tribune|date=18 April 2018|archive-date=2021-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210807044435/https://www.chicagotribune.com/columns/ryan-ori/ct-biz-hotel-indigo-redevelopment-ryan-ori-20180418-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>英迪格酒店品牌的第一個非美國飯店於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[渥太華|渥太華]]開業。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Ottawa Hotel Indigo to deflag and go independent|url=https://www.boutiquehotelnews.com/home/news/2017/1/18/ottawa-hotel-indigo-to-deflag-and-go-independent|access-date=26 February 2020|author=Sell|first=George|work=Boutique Hotels|archive-date=2020-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227000500/https://www.boutiquehotelnews.com/home/news/2017/1/18/ottawa-hotel-indigo-to-deflag-and-go-independent|dead-url=no}}</ref>
